data.description: You MUST see this beautifully updated and very large traditional home in the heart of Snellville! Complete with private back yard, sunroom, back deck, bedroom on the main, oversized master with ensuite, and fresh paint throughout! This home is perfect for a family looking for more space, or an investor looking for a cash flowing rental property in a great school district. Priced to sell!
